channel.title: Please! I dont know what this is!
channel.description:
Hi, I was working on a private server and I saw this:
[code=java]public transient IoSession session; [/code] And I thought to myself, "wtf is this?? How do I assign this to anything?" If anyone knows what this type of variable is, please respond
